\par 
\par Dear Sir or Madam:
\par 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\nooverflow\faroman\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\fs22 You are hereby directed to stop payment on the following check under the name: ____________________________.
\par 
