\par Amount of the check: $______________.
\par Payee of the check: __________________________________________
\par 
\par This order is made under and subject to the provisions of Section 4-403 of the Uniform Commercial Code of the State of ___________.}{\f1  
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\nooverflow\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\fs22 
